### /_authcheck
GET {{Host}}/_authcheck
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}


### /auth/sign-up
POST {{Host}}/auth/sign-up
content-type: application/json

{
    "email": "johnsmith@foobar.net",
    "password": "Password@1234",
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Smith",
    "groupName": "",
    "tos": "2024-04-16"
