# User

### /user
GET {{Host}}/user
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}


### /user
POST {{Host}}/user
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
content-type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Alex",
    "lastName": "Jones"
}


### /user/update-password
POST {{Host}}/user/update-password
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
content-type: application/json

{
    "password": "Password@1234",
    "newPassword": "NewPassword!4321"
}
